\- parameters live inside pipes and can appear anywhere in a node -\

@figure
|lamp.png|
|caption - The second-order Fresnel lens|
|full width|
figure@

\- three forms:
   |value|         positional
   |key - value|   named (everything left of the first - is the key)
   |flag|          boolean — present = true -\

@scene |location - INT. LIGHTHOUSE — LANTERN ROOM| |time - NIGHT|
The wick caught.
scene@

\- whitespace around the first hyphen is allowed —
   reads naturally as a label on an object -\

@panel | background colour - dark slate |
The lantern room was unlit.
panel@

\- last one wins, applied from that point forward in the flow -\

@scene
|mood - calm|
The harbour was still.
|mood - tense|
Then the bell began to ring.
scene@
